name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.port
description:
Default port that the ShuffleHandler will run on. ShuffleHandler
   is a service run at the NodeManager to facilitate transfers of intermediate
   Map outputs to requesting Reducers.

name: hadoop.security.kms.client.encrypted.key.cache.expiry
description:
Cache expiry time for a Key, after which the cache Queue for this
    key will be dropped. Default = 12hrs

name: dfs.webhdfs.netty.low.watermark
description: Low watermark configuration to Netty for Datanode WebHdfs.

name: dfs.ha.zkfc.nn.http.timeout.ms
description:
The HTTP connection and read timeout value (unit is ms ) when DFS ZKFC
    tries to get local NN thread dump after local NN becomes
    SERVICE_NOT_RESPONDING or SERVICE_UNHEALTHY.
    If it is set to zero, DFS ZKFC won't get local NN thread dump.

name: ha.health-monitor.sleep-after-disconnect.ms
description: How long to sleep after an unexpected RPC error.

name: dfs.client-write-packet-size
description: Packet size for clients to write

name: dfs.qjournal.queued-edits.limit.mb
description: Queue size in MB for quorum journal edits.
